Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:34.64,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscx75\blur3}Hide and seek so dangerous night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.50,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Tick tick tack 時計仕掛け above the 摩天楼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.54,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}そっと忍ばす {\fscx75}My heart is a trap and bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:46.84,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}Ah-ah-ah 群がる視線を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.88,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Who's the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.10,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}勝負は一度きり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.20,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今 火を点けて
