Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.64,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}誰かに盗られる前に ほら {\fscx75}Love is burning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.90,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}熱を感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:12.08,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}ヒリヒリと {\fscx100}刺激的{\fscx75}Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.08,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 150)\blur3\fs30\fsp-3}Feel it now, feel it now, feel it now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.22,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導火線の行方は風まかせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.02,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命の{\fscx75}Countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:18.04,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜風也茫然不解的旋律正在吹響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:22.54,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這既不是笑談也不是遊戲 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:30.16,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他人皆是對手 混沌的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:34.64,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}躲貓貓 如此危險的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.50,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘀嗒嘀嗒 摩天樓上時鐘作響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.54,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄然隱匿的 我心如陷阱與炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:46.84,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊啊 脫離成群的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.88,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倖存者會是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.10,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝負僅此一回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.20,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此刻 點燃烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:03:00.66,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步步地逼近 我所追求的更多賜予
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.64,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被他人盜走前 你看 愛在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.90,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觸到了熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:12.08,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火辣辣的 刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.08,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 180)\blur3\fs30}去感受它 去感受它 去感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.22,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導火線的行蹤就承載於風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.02,Undead OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命運的倒計時
